be.ac.ulb.infof307.g01.controller

Class MapController

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.ulb.infof307.g01.controller.MapController

  • public class MapController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller of the map. This class is responsible of creating markers at startup and when the user adds one. For that, it holds an instance of MarkerController, and forwards marker creation messages to the marker controller. It also holds the map view.
